<br>
1. Guild X mobilized before us and killed Mob_01.<br>
<br>
2. Guild X ganked Mob_01.<br>
<br>
3. Guild X KSed Mob_01.<br>
<br>
Statement 1 is a compliment.<br>
<br>
Statement 2 implies that Guild X did something moderately distasteful.<br>
<br>
Statement 3 implies that Guild X did something seriously wrong.<br>
<br>
You said:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr> Engaging a mob that is already engaged by another group/raid is called kill-stealing. <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
